{"tid":750642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友嗌交dum爛自己部電話","createTime":"2018-07-21T05:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T07:29:45.000Z","uid":135307,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e49f62ec1fbfd90bf7c92220e17a5c6706dfa414","tid":750642,"uid":135307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"琴晚同男朋友嗌交 佢嬲得濟 <br />\n自己dum爛咗自己部電話<br />\n我笑番佢on9 我有冇錯<br />\n定佢真係on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab780a7d8470141018a73cc6929d807f931a5c3","tid":750642,"uid":82450,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:31:53.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"154af8c81f62c23f9695228469ebcadc684f992d","tid":750642,"uid":135307,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/133217_ba22ea937da0d3bf28d44ce919f3840f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F133217_ba22ea937da0d3bf28d44ce919f3840f.png&h=b8198792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲零件仲值唔值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40472fc237acaf264589a4bd8e6411a1a5006ebd","tid":750642,"uid":144323,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"唔洗問，要整mon 唔該去返 apple"},{"pid":"f5420a23274a380a7f485bdcba1ff6ed9a1c5b18","tid":750642,"uid":4100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"佢真係on9"},{"pid":"08fcc28e776ac15b1a2b20fcad17358a6777e094","tid":750642,"uid":6959,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:33:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f78830aa4e9e8edbe91ce888adfd3b01b029ed1b","tid":750642,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:33:36.000Z","msg":"你on9"},{"pid":"adfadcefcdfa715d7e79af8fd1bee9a6e6c4ff46","tid":750642,"uid":135307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08fcc28e776ac15b1a2b20fcad17358a6777e094","tid":750642,"uid":6959,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:33:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"我好冷靜望住佢<br />\n佢就dum完一次見唔爛<br />\n再dum多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4dfbd5455f943290a8713f77d1a47c9273d1d4","tid":750642,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"9ac48f53bf77dcd3b91e43fea791fab4f8d9ce53","tid":750642,"uid":9286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"「喂呀！爛咗喇...」"},{"pid":"17ddfc02dc18bbba9ad516a10fcf9e2698b93e49","tid":750642,"uid":54930,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"我細妹中三 就俾人搞大咗個肚... <br />\n<br />\n因為我細妹本身好MK 我又要番學 根本冇時間管佢既生活 <br />\n<br />\n其實我地屋企從細到大都係咁 <br />\n<br />\n阿爸阿媽番工 放假就係屋企休息 基本上我地兩兄妹只要唔變壞就唔會去管我地 <br />\n<br />\n但係我細妹呢件事太大獲 阿媽激到想辭職留係屋企 管我細妹 <br />\n<br />\n大概係3~4個月前 我細妹佢玩game識到一個男人 <br />\n<br />\n然後果個男人咁岩又住係我地附近 <br />\n<br />\n年紀應該有3X歲 而且離過婚 聽講離婚係因為經常飲醉酒發酒癲 <br />\n<br />\n佢地好似係網上傾咗2~3個禮拜就見面了 <br />\n<br />\n而且第一日見面就上佢屋企啪啪啪了 <br />\n<br />\n之後每個假日 佢地都會見面上佢度啪啪啪 <br />\n<br />\n就係咁一直持續了3個月左右 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就同果個男人說講 她已經3個月冇黎m <br />\n<br />\n果個男人一開始話佢會負責 會黎我地屋企提親 <br />\n<br />\n估唔到講完呢句話 第二天就人間蒸發 手機都打不通 一直熄機 <br />\n<br />\n直到我細妹前日同我阿爸阿媽講呢件事 <br />\n<br />\n我爸媽前日夜晚12點 就衝去果個男人屋企撞門 <br />\n<br />\n要果個男人講清楚 而且準備告佢 果個男人話佢消失果兩個禮拜 係同朋友出國玩 <br />\n<br />\n咁岩今日番黎 準備要打俾我細妹 我地就衝咗過黎 <br />\n<br />\n我爸媽根本唔信 而且果個男人睇落窮酸樣 又住公屋 邊有錢出國玩 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就一直喊一直喊 <br />\n<br />\n果晚我阿媽俾咗枝驗孕棒俾我細妹用 真係大咗肚 <br />\n<br />\n琴晚我知道咗件事之後 請咗一日假 同我細妹傾下 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就話果個男人對佢好好 點點點咁 <br />\n<br />\n我根本就聽唔入耳 我就話 對你好 只不過係想呃你隻豬 <br />\n<br />\n一講完呢句 我細妹就喊 然後將枱面部iPhone掟落地 成個moon爆咗 <br />\n<br />\n所以我想下各位巴打 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知邊度整番個moon好 <br />\n<br />\nTHX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2eb227f5488da1b1e1117f38d41ddbfe241374","tid":750642,"uid":140831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"兩個男人嘈到咁都冇打出手算係咁"},{"pid":"0b6298f007400f7e73d00b9766c01ba8f72033f8","tid":750642,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"真係好on9"},{"pid":"f4e3b6a91dbc4251afa1874a916ecb464f29241f","tid":750642,"uid":135307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aa2eb227f5488da1b1e1117f38d41ddbfe241374","tid":750642,"uid":140831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"兩個男人嘈到咁都冇打出手算係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"真絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa82ad08c9c71c8d2a21eee90d72b40cebe963c","tid":750642,"uid":135307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab780a7d8470141018a73cc6929d807f931a5c3","tid":750642,"uid":82450,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:31:53.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ef09cafd4b7a0872676afc3be19e9b7bf4059e","tid":750642,"uid":135307,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"17ddfc02dc18bbba9ad516a10fcf9e2698b93e49","tid":750642,"uid":54930,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"我細妹中三 就俾人搞大咗個肚... <br />\n<br />\n因為我細妹本身好MK 我又要番學 根本冇時間管佢既生活 <br />\n<br />\n其實我地屋企從細到大都係咁 <br />\n<br />\n阿爸阿媽番工 放假就係屋企休息 基本上我地兩兄妹只要唔變壞就唔會去管我地 <br />\n<br />\n但係我細妹呢件事太大獲 阿媽激到想辭職留係屋企 管我細妹 <br />\n<br />\n大概係3~4個月前 我細妹佢玩game識到一個男人 <br />\n<br />\n然後果個男人咁岩又住係我地附近 <br />\n<br />\n年紀應該有3X歲 而且離過婚 聽講離婚係因為經常飲醉酒發酒癲 <br />\n<br />\n佢地好似係網上傾咗2~3個禮拜就見